author: ate
msg: Re-enabling PortletResourceURLFactory handling (pre Portlet API 2.0 ResourceURL solution served on a RenderURL) which was "broken" with the upgrade to Pluto 2.0
This now again allows full control over the (Render) response like setting content-type, so supporting streaming out binary output too (for instance dynamic images, pdf, etc.)
